---
// Fixed bottom-right "back to the mirror" link.
// Used on every non-home page so the home is always one click away.
---
<a class="back-link" href="/">← back to the mirror</a>

<style>
  .back-link {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    z-index: 10;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    opacity: 0.6;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }
  .back-link:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }
</style>
